 class=\"summary-title-link\" href=\"\/blog\/bestusefultravelapps2019\">The Best Travel Apps That You&#8217;ll Actually Use In 2019 | For finding flights, hotels, vegan food, &amp; more.<\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-title\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n                  summary-excerpt\n                  summary-excerpt-only\n                \"><\/p>\n<p style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Travel agent, <em>WHO? <\/em> These are the best travel apps in 2019 that you\u2019ll actually use.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-content\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          summary-item\n          summary-item-record-type-text\n          sqs-gallery-design-carousel-slide\n\n            summary-item-has-thumbnail\n\n           summary-item-has-excerpt\n          summary-item-has-cats\n          summary-item-has-tags\n          summary-item-has-author\n          summary-item-has-comments-enabled\n          \"><\/p>\n<div class=\"summary-thumbnail-outer-container\">\n<div class=\"summary-thumbnail img-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<p><!-- Main Image --><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"summary-thumbnail-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/IMG_1116.jpg\" alt=\"When Strangers From The Internet Make Magic | A VIDEO\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/IMG_1116.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"1242x1550\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.505859375,0.54\" data-load=\"false\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><!-- Products: Quick View --><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-content sqs-gallery-meta-container\" data-animation-role=\"content\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--above-title\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-title\"><a class=\"summary-title-link\" href=\"\/blog\/meetpeopletravelsolo\">When Strangers From The Internet Make Magic | A VIDEO<\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-title\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n                  summary-excerpt\n                  summary-excerpt-only\n                \"><\/p>\n<p style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is what happens when you book a last-minute flight to London and meet up with strangers from the internet<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata-container summary-metadata-container--below-content\">\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--primary\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"summary-metadata summary-metadata--secondary\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          summary-item\n          summary-item-record-type-text\n          sqs-gallery-design-carousel-slide\n\n            summary-item-has-thumbnail\n\n           summary-item-has-excerpt\n          summary-item-has-cats\n          summary-item-has-tags\n          summary-item-has-author\n          summary-item-has-comments-enabled\n          \"><\/p>\n<div class=\"summary-thumbnail-outer-container\">\n<div class=\"summary-thumbnail img-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<p><!-- Main Image --><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"summary-thumbnail-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Facetune_09-12-2018-20-10-05-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"I WAS FEATURED IN A PODCAST | Traveling As A Black Woman\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Facetune_09-1